item.title: CVE-2023-30518|2024-08-02T14:28:51.924Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20thycotic%20secret%20server%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Thycotic Secret Server Plugin 1.0.2 and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of credentials stored in Jenkins.
